sailpoint.object

Class Attributes<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.AbstractMap<K,V>
      • java.util.HashMap<K,V>
        • sailpoint.object.Attributes<K,V>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.util.Map<K,V>, sailpoint.tools.xml.PersistentXmlObject

    public class Attributes<K,V>
extends java.util.HashMap<K,V>
implements sailpoint.tools.xml.PersistentXmlObject
    An extension of HashMap that adds convenience coercion methods. This class is used throughout the model to represent collections of dynamic attributes.
    See Also:
